Docker Toolbox: http://192.168.99.100
===================
start a new container with: run
start an old container: start
docker run -dp 80:80 nginx
docker run --name fart -dp 80:80 nginx
docker top fart
docker rm <id> -f
docker ps
docker container ls 
docker container ls -a
docker stop <id>
docker container stop <id>
docker logs <id>

